{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act18d3_level_act18d3_04_beg","storyGroup":"act18d3","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"act18d3_level_act18d3_03_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"SV-4","storyName":"海洋","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"摆脱年轻审判官的斯卡蒂遭遇了另一名更年长的审判官，双方交手后，斯卡蒂流血逃走。很快，海里的怪物找上了她。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act18d3/level_act18d3_04_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act18d3_04","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["斯卡蒂","审判官","大审判官","安妮塔","主教","歌蕾蒂娅","男性居民C","男性居民D","男性居民B","怪物A","怪物B","怪物C"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ibtownn","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$tense_intro","key":"$tense_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","fadetime":"1.5","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"长官！","id":16},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"退下。你不是她的对手。","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"但是我......","id":20},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"退下。","id":22},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"遵命！","id":24},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":27},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","fadetime":"0.7","id":29},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂与面前的人隔着十来米，静静地对视。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":31},{"type":"subtitle","id":32},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你，强很多。","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"你不该踏入这座城市。","id":37},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我已经在了。","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"违背规则，就要付出代价。","id":41},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我管不了那么多。","id":43},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"你会留在这里。","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......我不想同你打。","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#3","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"哼。邪恶的阿戈尔人，你一定是害怕了！有长官在，你绝对跑不掉。","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"但，如果这是必须的话——","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"（阿戈尔语）我将打败你。","id":52},{"type":"dialog","id":53},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.6","id":55},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"起步，加速，冲击。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":57},{"type":"subtitle","id":58},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"好快，竟比刚才和我交手时候还要快许多！","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"如果是这样的速度，我根本就连她的裙摆都打不中......她到底还藏了多少？！","id":63},{"type":"dialog","id":64},{"type":"character","id":65},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":66},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":67},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":68},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"在撞上大审判官之前，斯卡蒂退开了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":69},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她像一条被海浪冲上半空的鱼，高高跃起，又落在残破的屋顶。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":70},{"type":"subtitle","id":71},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":72},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":73},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":75},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"大审判官如影随形。两人身形相撞，又退开，再次相撞。本就千疮百孔的城镇难以经受这样的冲击，街道上建筑物的碎片正在迅速增多。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":76},{"type":"subtitle","id":77},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"character","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"攻击和闪避都越来越快，老师也是。我就要跟不上了。","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"原来我......我还差这么多？！","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"不，这不行。那可是一个阿戈尔人。我才不能输给阿戈尔人。","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"可是这个阿戈尔人，她好像，还在拿着她的箱子当武器......那箱子是什么做的啊！为什么那么硬？！","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"不过，老师也没有用手炮。要是用上的话......瞬间就能把她拿下吧？连着这条街一起，都会一起被轰成渣。","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"然而......那只是一个阿戈尔人啊？她的模样，和那些怪物并不一样......","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"她用的是......某种法术吗？我感觉不出来。我们的灯......也并没有能压制她的力量。","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"——这阿戈尔人身上藏着的秘密太多了。","id":91},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":93},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"3","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":94},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_explo_n","id":95},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":101},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"整条街的震动渐渐停止了。碎屑与烟尘之中，年长的审判官再次现身。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":104},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","fadetime":"1","id":105},{"type":"subtitle","id":106},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"......","id":109},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#7","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"长官！您果然赢了。我就知道，任何人都无法撼动您分毫。","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"咦，那个阿戈尔人呢？","id":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"逃了。","id":114},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"什么？这......怎么会？","id":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"她受伤了，跑不了多远。","id":118},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我去找她——","id":120},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"你打不过她。","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#3","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"咳咳......但绝不能让她这样的人在这片海岸恣意行走！","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"看方向，她应该是去居民聚居处了。她可能混入人群，当地居民之中有人在帮她。我会一间一间屋子找过去。","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"如果你认为这是对的，你就去。","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"好——","id":129},{"type":"dialog","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":131},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"$suspenseful_loop","volume":"0.4","id":132,"musicid":1},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"......","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"长官，这座城市的异状，是她带来的吗？","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"我让你去看。你看到了什么？","id":136},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"这座城市里的人，他们的行为很不正常。每天就像没有醒着的时候。他们行动，却不是为了到达。他们进食，甚至不是为了饱腹。","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"他们正在往海里走，而且他们并不认为这是自杀。","id":139},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"你制止了他们？","id":141},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"是。因为这显然是错的。","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"我们关心的，是结果。你认为你的纠正能有对的结果，那就去做。","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"对的结果......","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"若不能，那你必须有所选择。","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"判官——你的双眼，你的剑，需紧盯伊比利亚最大的威胁。","id":150},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"是，长官！","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"最大的威胁......是那些正在上岸的怪物。","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"难道说，这些正在走向大海的人，他们与这些怪物有什么联系？","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"对......一定有联系。","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"老师说过，异常往往不是单一现象。这些恐怖的异象之间，必有关联。","id":156},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"要解决问题——你首先要看清问题所在。","id":158},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我、我知道！","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"——是那些躲在暗中谋划一切的阿戈尔人！","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"他们潜伏在岸上，躲藏在我们律法的缝隙里，腐化我们城市的皮肉，动摇我们同胞的心志，试图侵蚀我们国家的筋骨。","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"在他们的阴谋得逞、将这座城市拖入绝望的深渊之前——","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我们必须，将他们找出，抹除！","id":164},{"type":"Dialog","id":165},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":167},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":168},{"type":"Character","id":169},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ibindoor","id":170},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":171},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"$ponder_loop","volume":"0.4","id":172,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":174},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":175},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","fadetime":"1","id":176},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"歌手......歌手？你是不是在这里？","id":178},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#2","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":180},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"我找了你好久。审判官一定不知道这地方，这里空屋子太多啦，到了晚上，可不好找。","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"我知道......你肯定想躲着我们。你想离我们住的地方越远越好。","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"找到这里可真不容易......呼......这儿离海岸好近。","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"这是海浪的声音吗？原来这么大。还有......我听到了呼吸声。","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"歌手，你在这里做什么？你的吸气声音变得不大一样。","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#2","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你们有危险。","id":188},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#2","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"你说什么......呃，你怎么，你受了伤？","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#2","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我流血了。快走！","id":192},{"type":"dialog","id":193},{"type":"character","id":194},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":195},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":196},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#3","fadetime":"1","id":198},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"想走？没那么容易。","id":200},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","focus":"1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"审判官？！难道是跟着我一路过来的......我、我没有发现。","id":202},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":203},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"$suspenseful_loop","volume":"0.4","id":204,"musicid":3},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我还不至于让一个普通人发现。咳，当然，即便不跟踪你，我也一样有法子找到这里！","id":205},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"又是你。","id":207},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"怎么，是怕了吗？","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"刚才，咳咳，我承认，我一时疏忽，险些让你逃走。","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"但现在，阿戈尔人，我一定会将你抓住！","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","focus":"1","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"可、可是，她已经受伤了——","id":213},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#3","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"嗯？你确定要拦下我，保护这个危险的阿戈尔人吗，市民？这样的话，你会变成和她一样的罪犯！","id":215},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","focus":"1","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"我、我......","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"你和其他人都不一样。至少，你眼里还有害怕。","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"到现在为止，你还没有做错事。快闪开！我也不想用剑对付你。","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","name2":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"不是时候——","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"不是什么时候？你......你瞧不起我？你以为我一定没法拿下你？","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"哼，我确实不是长官。可我也已经做好了准备。","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"对付你，我会全力以赴！","id":226},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":228},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"剑未出鞘，斯卡蒂便摁住了审判官的手臂——将她拉到了自己身后。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":231},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#3","id":232},{"type":"subtitle","id":233},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"你、你什么意思？","id":237},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"不要出声。","id":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"2","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"放开我，你这个阿戈尔混蛋，你别以为按着我的手我就没办法用剑，我还有手炮——","id":241},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"1","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"别吵。它们会发现。","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#3","focus":"2","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"唔唔唔......另一只手也......动不了......","id":245},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":246,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#4","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"呃，你们听，是不是有声音？","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"我听见了......黏糊糊的东西在地上摩擦......有好多好多......好像就在外面。","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"这是......什么啊？不是我们的人弄出来的，我以前从来都没有听过......","id":250},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#3","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"越来越近了。","id":252},{"type":"Dialog","id":253},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_183#3","id":256},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ibcoastn","id":257},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"数量，在增长。","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"是什么引起的？这里的人，还是她们？","id":261},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":264},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":266},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"十只——","id":269},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":272},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":274},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":276},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":277},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":279},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"二十只。","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"——仍在增长，仍在前进。有什么在吸引它们爬上海岸，涌进城内。","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"而来的方向是——","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"大审判官","text":"教堂。","id":285},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":287},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":289},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":291},{"type":"Dialog","id":292},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"image","id":295},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","id":296},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":299},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"1","id":300},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"嗯？他们很兴奋。","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......你确定要像这样抚摸这些东西？","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"注意你使用的词语。他们可不是什么“东西”。他们已经是这片大海的一部分，成为了海的子嗣，比你要纯净得多。","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"啊......潮汐的讯息已至。今夜又是特别的。","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"他们一定是闻见了气味。当有同胞加入时，他们总会变得很雀跃，很躁动，甚至想浮出海面，去陆上迎接。","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"这很正常。我们都爱着自己的兄弟姐妹。","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#2","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"2","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你真当它们是你的兄弟？","id":313},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#2","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"为什么不呢？在需要的时候，我也愿称陆上那些仍不得不用双足行走的为兄弟。","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"如果你不是拥有最脏污的杂种血脉，有朝一日，你也能拥有这种机会。","id":316},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"2","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"哦？那真是可惜。","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.35","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","blackstart2":"0.3","blackend2":"0.45","focus":"1","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"（触碰海水）","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"有趣。今天晚上......他们好像格外有精神。或许因为有很多新老朋友都来家里做客。","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"主教","text":"你不好奇么？上面究竟在发生什么。","id":322},{"type":"Dialog","id":323},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"character","id":326},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ibindoor","id":327},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","id":328},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":329},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":331},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.7","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"1","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民C","text":"......吵。","id":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"2","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民D","text":"真的吵。睡不着。","id":337},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"1","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民C","text":"把头塞在被子里。","id":339},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"2","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民D","text":"听不见。","id":341},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"1","id":342},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民C","text":"看不见。","id":343},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_187","id":344},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民B","text":"......","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民B","text":"呜......好饿......","id":347},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"1","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民C","text":"好饿。","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_188","name2":"avg_npc_189","focus":"2","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民D","text":"好饿。","id":351},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_187","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"男性居民B","text":"铁皮......","id":353},{"type":"Dialog","id":354},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":355},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":356},{"type":"character","id":357},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":358},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ibindoor","id":359},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":361},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","id":362},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":363},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":364},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","id":365},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":366},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":367},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$warchaos_intro","key":"$warchaos_loop","volume":"0.4","id":368,"musicid":5},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"啊！","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":371},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"呜哇哇——","id":372},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"来了。","id":374},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"这、这是什么鬼东西啊？！黑色的......花？还是鱼？为什么会动？好恶心，呕......","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"难道是......不对啊，这说不通！","id":377},{"type":"dialog","id":378},{"type":"character","id":379},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","id":380},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":381},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":382},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","id":383},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":384},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":385},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"它们在拍窗！它们是不是......是不是想进来？！","id":387},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"不、不能让它们进来！","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"把窗关紧——","id":390},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"没用的，这里的窗本来就是破的，你看上面，到处都是缝......","id":392},{"type":"dialog","id":393},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":394},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bottlebroken","id":395},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":396},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":397},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"——伸进来了！","id":398},{"type":"dialog","id":399},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":400},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":401},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":402},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":403},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":405},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"呜哇，它还在动！就这一小块，趴在地上扭来扭去，朝我们不断地挤过来？！","id":406},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"就算是那种东西......也不该这么难缠啊！","id":407},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"太多了......外面还有好多。","id":409},{"type":"dialog","id":410},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","id":411},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":412},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":413},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":414},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":416},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":417},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":418},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":419},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":420},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"1","id":422},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":423},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":424},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","id":425},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"这怎么都砍不完！","id":426},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我的灯......不行，灯对它们没什么用处。","id":427},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"......弹药只够再打一发。","id":428},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":429},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"审、审判官？！","id":430},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","id":431},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"别动！待会我一开炮，你们俩就往里边跑。废墟总比这破窗牢一点。","id":432},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_180#2","id":433},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"你的手在抖......","id":434},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#2","id":435},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"神圣的经文......将给我力量。","id":436},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我、我不怕它们！","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"我马上出去，能杀多少是多少，应该能挡上一阵，你们要跑快一点......","id":438},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":439},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":440},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#2","focus":"1","id":441},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你，带着她躲到里面去。","id":442},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"2","id":443},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"啊？你在说什么啊！你没看见吗？我对付不了——这么多！很快它们都会进来。屋里和屋外没有区别！","id":444},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"1","id":445},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"记住，离门窗越远越好。","id":446},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_182#4","focus":"2","id":447},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"你这人根本不听别人讲话——","id":448},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":449},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我会出去。把它们引开。","id":450},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","name2":"avg_npc_180#2","focus":"1","id":451},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"什么？！","id":452},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","name2":"avg_npc_180#4","focus":"2","id":453},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"歌手，你也不能出去啊......","id":454},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"你是很厉害，比我见过的人都要厉害，但你受伤了呀！而且这些怪东西，可、可太多啦！","id":455},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"审判官也、也别出去了......","id":456},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#5","name2":"avg_npc_180#2","focus":"2","id":457},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安妮塔","text":"我们一起躲躲？我、我知道这里有个橱柜，还能关上门，就在后头，我们三个人挤挤，应该也能......","id":458},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":459},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我必须出去。只有这样，你们才能活。","id":460},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_182#4","name2":"avg_npc_180#4","focus":"1","id":461},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"审判官","text":"喂，阿戈尔人，就算要逞英雄，这里也轮不到你！","id":462},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":463},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":464},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"听好。这真的不关你的事。","id":465},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"因为——它们是来找我的。","id":466},{"type":"dialog","id":467},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":468},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":469},{"type":"dialog","id":470},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":471},{"type":"Character","id":472},{"type":"Image","image":"ac18_04","fadetime":"0","id":473},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":474},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":476},{"type":"Text","text":"斯卡蒂推开门。","id":477},{"type":"Text","text":"久违的气味自海风吹来的方向钻入脑髓，从不属于陆地的生物密密麻麻地填满了街道。","id":478},{"type":"Text","text":"它们上下涌动着，吐息，缩紧，用行为模拟腐烂和生长，文明的疆岸在它们险恶的身躯下陷落。","id":479},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_185","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":480},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"怪物A","text":"......","id":481},{"type":"dialog","id":482},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_185","name2":"avg_npc_185","fadetime":"1","id":483},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"怪物B","text":"......","id":484},{"type":"dialog","id":485},{"type":"character","id":486},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":487},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_185","fadetime":"0.6","id":488},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"怪物C","text":"！！！","id":489},{"type":"dialog","id":490},{"type":"character","id":491},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":492},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":494},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","fadetime":"1","id":495},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂向前再走了一步。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":496},{"type":"subtitle","id":497},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g"